gfc:definition.gco:CharacterString: Current American Indian/Alaska Native/ Native Hawaiian area identifier; a concatenation of Current American Indian/Alaska Native/Native Hawaiian area census code and reservation/statistical area or off-reservation trust land Hawaiianhome land indicator

The GEOID attribute is a concatenation of the Current American Indian/Alaska Native/Native Hawaiian Area census code ("AIANNHCE" attribute) followed by the reservation/statistical area or off-reservation trust land indicator ("COMPTYP" attribute). No spaces are allowed between the two codes.
